245
00:18:46,589 --> 00:18:48,520
kemudian menemui Profesor Lee.

246
00:18:50,659 --> 00:18:51,859
Apa yang kamu lakukan?

247
00:18:52,030 --> 00:18:54,059
"Profesor Lee"

248
00:18:54,829 --> 00:18:57,030
