mungkin aku akhirnya mendapat jawaban.

375
00:29:38,940 --> 00:29:40,010
Pak?

376
00:29:40,369 --> 00:29:41,909
Ya, silakan masuk.

377
00:29:45,510 --> 00:29:46,980
Ada paket untuk Anda.

378
00:29:47,849 --> 00:29:48,879
Terima kasih.

379
00:29:48,879 --> 00:29:50,520
Nama ini menunjukkan paketnya dari wanita.

380
00:30:00,829 --> 00:30:02,899
"Pengirim, Lee Ham Suk"

381
00:30:02,899 --> 00:30:04,000
Lee Ham Suk?

382
00:30:17,609 --> 00:30:18,609
Selamat datang.

383
00:30:19,980 --> 00:30:21,220
Anda ingin membeli hadiah?

384
00:30:22,379 --> 00:30:23,379
Ya.

385
00:30:24,919 --> 00:30:26,319
Anda ingin membeli apa?

386
00:30:27,520 --> 00:30:28,589
Mantel.

387
00:30:29,419 --> 00:30:32,829
Mantel mewah yang ingin kamu pakai,

388
00:30:33,159 --> 00:30:36,899
tapi terlalu malu untuk memakainya di pedesaan.

389
00:30:37,329 --> 00:30:38,599
Bisakah kamu memberi saran?

390
00:30:38,700 --> 00:30:41,099
Apa? Aku tidak paham maksud Anda.

