456
00:38:21,660 --> 00:38:25,100
Dia bersemangat tanpa perlu mencemaskan putranya lagi.

457
00:38:25,100 --> 00:38:28,470
Peri Seon sepertinya mempelajari semua resep

458
00:38:28,470 --> 00:38:30,539
hidangan kesukaan Geum darinya.

459
00:38:36,240 --> 00:38:38,609
Saat itu Geum berusia 5 tahun.

460
00:38:38,910 --> 00:38:40,879
Dia keluar untuk bermain,

461
00:38:41,379 --> 00:38:43,479
tapi tidak pulang hingga larut malam.

462
00:38:43,479 --> 00:38:46,950
Jadi, aku mencari dia bersama para warga desa.

463
00:38:47,689 --> 00:38:49,760
Kami mencari dia di mana pun

464
00:38:51,490 --> 00:38:54,060
dan ternyata

465
00:38:54,060 --> 00:38:56,060
dia tertidur di gunung.

466
00:39:03,269 --> 00:39:05,740
Dia tertidur di semak-semak

467
00:39:05,970 --> 00:39:09,709
dan aku merasakan angin hangat

468
00:39:09,709 --> 00:39:12,580
dan cahaya remang-remang di sekitar dia.

469
00:39:12,749 --> 00:39:15,120
